The NEWS file for the vpick package.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1.1.1rc0 -- 10 March 2025

Changes:
   Added the ability to toggle viewer windows off and on from the command
   buttons.

   Added a 'Raise Viewer' option to the right-hand menu on the host buttons.

   Many bugfixes to code for handling window positioning.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1.1.0rc0 -- 20 February 2025

Changes:
   Runtime Options. Added a '--screen' switch to vpick(1).
   
   Viewier Window Positions. Added the ability to the desktop build to set a
   default position for each host window.

   Viewer Buttons. Added a setting to the desktop build to allow different
   actions when toggling a viewer button.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1.0.0rc2 -- 2 August 2024

Changes:
   Added a '--display-profile' switch to vpick(1).
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1.0.0rc2 -- 1 August 2024

Changes:
   Fixed a bug in the 'Host Settings' dialog that failed to properly
   initialize the state of the 'Show Password' checkbox.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1.0.0rc1 -- 25 July 2024

Changes:
   Fixed a bug in the vpick(1) destktop entry file. See the ChangeLog
   for details.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1.0.0rc0 -- 25 July 2024

Changes:
   The first "official" release.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
